description: After six weeks indoors, under-14s are being let out of doors, but how damaging was the lockdown?
title: Coronavirus: Spain's children run free from lockdown - but not all
title_page: Coronavirus: Spain's children run free from lockdown - but not all - BBC News
maintext: Six weeks later, having not left the family's flat once, the lockdown has lost some of its shine for him and he still does not know when he will be able to go out.
